---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="教程 | DORA 中文社区" description="DORA 入门教程与学习路径（持续完善）。">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">教程</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
      这里会沉淀从 0 到 1 的中文学习路径：安装、数据流配置、常用节点与调试方法。
      当前页面是骨架版本，后续会逐步补充可直接运行的示例与配套说明。
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <a
        href="https://dora-rs.ai/docs/guides/Installation/installing"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md"
      >
        <div class="text-base font-semibold text-[#000063]">安装</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">pip、脚本、Cargo、Docker 等与官网一致。</div>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://dora-rs.ai/docs/guides/getting-started/conversation_py"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md"
      >
        <div class="text-base font-semibold text-[#000063]">Getting Started</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">从对话式示例入门数据流与节点。</div>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://dora-rs.ai/docs/api/dataflow-config"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md"
      >
        <div class="text-base font-semibold text-[#000063]">数据流配置</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">YAML 声明式图结构与参数。</div>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://dora-rs.ai/docs/guides"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md"
      >
        <div class="text-base font-semibold text-[#000063]">全部 Guides</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">开发、调试、ROS2 桥接等专题。</div>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/examples"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:shadow-md"
      >
        <div class="text-base font-semibold text-[#000063]">本站示例索引</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">中文场景化示例（持续补充）。</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

